	  scheduling, IPI dispatch, and per-CPU arrays remain native
	  Zephyr C.
	  Requires a Rust toolchain for the target architecture.

config GALE_KERNEL_KHEAP
	bool "Use Gale formally verified kheap"
	help
	  Use Gale formally verified byte-level allocation tracking for
	  kernel/kheap.c. Allocation and free byte counting with overflow
	  and underflow protection are handled by verified Rust code.
	  sys_heap internals, free-list, coalescing, wait queues, and
	  tracing remain native Zephyr C.
	  Requires a Rust toolchain for the target architecture.

